data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Providing a statistics web interface for Plex & Sonarr.
Use the other tabs to configure Sonarr, Plex and the web interface. Sonarr and Plex will attempt to connect locally to their respective API endpoints. Plex needs a roundtrip to Plex.tv first to retrieve an authorization key to do this. All data is stored locally and the settings are encrypted in your userdata appdata folder; they survive updates.

data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value:
Use the private PIN for accessing the web interface and android app yourself. Give the public PIN to friends and people you want to be able to check out your calendar.
You need network forwarding to the port you assign. Turn on/off webserver by add/remove a port and save. The android app can be downloaded at https://thronic.com
